{"tid":744857,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蛀港共軍青少年夏令營展開　參與500學生不懼洗腦教育 期望放假不止打機","createTime":"2018-07-16T09:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T13:37:26.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"470dce94f758c7264ffce9e95cb6125d801d3fe1","tid":744857,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:18:10.000Z","msg":"香港青少年軍事夏令營在新圍軍營舉行開營典禮，500名香港中學生入營接受訓練，為期15日。今年新增設中一、中二體驗班，共有5日訓練。<br />\n<br />\n解放軍駐港部隊副司令員田永江指，希望學員能夠了解香港駐軍、國家軍事及國防知識，並培養健康體魄，為將來貢獻香港及國家打好基礎。<br />\n<br />\n其中一名參加訓練營的中四學生指，不擔心被洗腦，亦不怕會有洗腦教育，因為營中不會故意灌輸一些訊息，只會培訓團隊精神，反而擔心自己體能難以應付，期待參觀一些軍艦及軍槍示範。<br />\n<br />\n另一名中三學生表示，自己經常打機，希望參加軍營規劃自己。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1407217-20180716.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1407217-20180716.htm&d=nMFf4G2X1VZq%2Bl%2B5tUcDgYS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=b8973863\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1407217-20180716.htm&h=2666a78a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1407217-20180716.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0b938662cd19b6308c4679d76a2a95752f9906d6","tid":744857,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:19:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/16/171908_16375df3b4dee56b4438f164cb720722.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F16%2F171908_16375df3b4dee56b4438f164cb720722.gif&h=36836cb2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b92e7db564107424bfe1a48a1c0593f0c863ef8","tid":744857,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T09:19:16.000Z","msg":"呢班00後 有前途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c3857c60d4c88d8bed1bcfe8e8d04cb208b1866","tid":744857,"uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-